      <p class="text-neutral-600">
        If you develop a new condition while covered by SafetyWing, initial emergency treatment may be covered. But ongoing management of that condition wouldn't be—it would become a "pre-existing condition" for future coverage purposes. This is where travel medical insurance shows its limitations.
      </p>
